{"tid":1037434,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"同老婆用長命契買左樓，如果想再買，係咪無首置免稅？","createTime":"2019-02-26T02:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T16:52:56.000Z","uid":46266,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"95e162ca5d821396382d020b4bb0bab910f1a2b9","tid":1037434,"uid":46266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:48:02.000Z","msg":"如題。<br />\n同老婆以長命契共同擁有一個單位。<br />\n因為想再買樓。<br />\n我地可唔可以將單位轉名俾一個人全權擁有，然後另一個買樓有無首置免稅？"},{"pid":"064085b10a4b3ccc2305865814232da6abde2bc1","tid":1037434,"uid":76960,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"搵律師搞轉名, 不過一樣要俾稅"},{"pid":"fcf875c5fef460aee30f9a6210fee48b28f9a49d","tid":1037434,"uid":46266,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"064085b10a4b3ccc2305865814232da6abde2bc1","tid":1037434,"uid":76960,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"搵律師搞轉名, 不過一樣要俾稅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:55:07.000Z","msg":"謝謝回覆，不過唔明😂😂😂😂<br />\n因為依家想換樓，因為有小朋友。<br />\n咁嗰時結婚冇諗咁多野，心諗太太有份供樓，咪用長命契買樓囉。<br />\n但依家想換樓，又好似貴左。"},{"pid":"527120dd1c7608a428f787a23db94d41df733aa3","tid":1037434,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcf875c5fef460aee30f9a6210fee48b28f9a49d","tid":1037434,"uid":46266,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"064085b10a4b3ccc2305865814232da6abde2bc1","tid":1037434,"uid":76960,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"搵律師搞轉名, 不過一樣要俾稅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:55:07.000Z","msg":"謝謝回覆，不過唔明😂😂😂😂<br />\n因為依家想換樓，因為有小朋友。<br />\n咁嗰時結婚冇諗咁多野，心諗太太有份供樓，咪用長命契買樓囉。<br />\n但依家想換樓，又好似貴左。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:56:45.000Z","msg":"兩個大人做過業主 除非用阿仔名買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7bf3d1e1690dddb5a8a08b632ba50647772fa6a","tid":1037434,"uid":18740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T02:57:29.000Z","msg":"你轉俾你老婆 俾一次S.D.先，應該3%左右睇樓價，